ZH: 我们轮流做家务。
EN: We take turns doing housework.

ZH: 请大家轮流发表意见。
EN: Please take turns expressing opinions.

ZH: 他们轮流照顾孩子。
EN: They take turns taking care of the children.

ZH: 我们参加了轮船游览。
EN: We went on a cruise.

ZH: 轮到你了。
EN: It's your turn now.

ZH: 请注意交通轮流通行。
EN: Please pay attention to traffic flow.

ZH: 他们轮换了工作岗位。
EN: They rotated job positions.

ZH: 不要打断别人讲话，要轮到你说话再说。
EN: Don't interrupt others, wait for it to be your turn to speak.

ZH: 我们轮着去喊外卖。
EN: We take turns ordering takeout.

